{"tid":1099072,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"（做孝子）想幫媽買2張鄭秀文","createTime":"2019-04-09T13:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T12:33:43.000Z","uid":75578,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d211d6bdbda230b16386697ee882c09fafb1a511","tid":1099072,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TVyS6t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6TVyS6t.png&h=c33f66c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽幾日前語重心長同我講<br />\n好想睇鄭秀文..<br />\n佢最鐘意就係Sammi <br />\n但係我今日返工突然要Training 幫唔到佢禁..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打多左2張380 任何位置同時間<br />\n比佢睇一睇, 完成心願, 只要2張自用，絕不轉售<br />\n（其實我完全唔鐘意Sammi，但都會想陪佢睇）<br />\nTg: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/J72728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FJ72728&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=1b976321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/J72728</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n上年呢個時間買到8張黃子華棟篤笑, 2張自用<br />\n6張堅原價賣比巴打...（車馬費都無收）<br />\n希望今次輪到我善有善報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabe8730529285fb1159814eb1ec6c2ab0d6f0bc","tid":1099072,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:20:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b62421e908bda92a07195f4f89ea9011ae98a09e","tid":1099072,"uid":1354,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:22:28.000Z","msg":"黃牛新手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ae5ad6f9fad7c1b37464e754bc3e95095927e7","tid":1099072,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b62421e908bda92a07195f4f89ea9011ae98a09e","tid":1099072,"uid":1354,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:22:28.000Z","msg":"黃牛新手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/p